@startuml
title Diagrama de Sequências - Ronda Completa (Refatorado)

actor Jogador
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "WebSocket" as WS
participant "Game" as Game
participant "Round" as Round
participant "Deck" as Deck
participant "Trick" as Trick
participant "EventBus" as EB

== Início da Ronda ==
Game -> Round : criar ronda

Round -> Deck : baralhar cartas
Deck --> Round : cartas baralhadas

Round -> EB : Notify(RoundStartedEvent)
EB -> WS : broadcast
WS -> FE : iniciar UI da ronda

Round -> Deck : revelar trunfo
Deck --> Round : carta de trunfo

Round -> EB : Notify(TrumpRevealedEvent)
EB -> WS : broadcast
WS -> FE : mostrar trunfo

Round -> Deck : distribuir cartas
Deck --> Round : cartas distribuídas

loop para cada jogador
    Round -> EB : Notify(CardDealtEvent)
    EB -> WS : broadcast
    WS -> FE : mostrar cartas
end

== Vaza ==
loop até ronda terminar

    Round -> Trick : criar nova vaza

    loop 4 jogadas (1 por jogador)

        Jogador -> FE : jogar carta
        FE -> WS : send(PlayCardCommand)

        WS -> Game : PlayCard(playerId, cardId)
        Game -> Round : processar jogada

        Round -> Trick : AddPlay()

        Round -> EB : Notify(CardPlayedEvent)
        EB -> WS : broadcast
        WS -> FE : atualizar mesa

    end

    Trick --> Round : Winner + pontos

    Round -> EB : Notify(TrickEndedEvent)
    EB -> WS : broadcast
    WS -> FE : mostrar vencedor da vaza

end

== Fim da Ronda ==

Round -> Round : verificar se terminou
note right : Lógica interna de\nverificação de fim de ronda

Round -> EB : Notify(RoundEndedEvent)
EB -> WS : broadcast
WS -> FE : mostrar pontuações

@enduml